DESCRIPTION:Join us on Wednesday\, June 10\, from 4-7 PM at Whispering Vine South Creek for a Jeff Runquist tasting featuring four California reds across Zinfandel\, Petite Sirah\, Barbera and Cabernet Franc.\nTasting Fee: $25 per person (Buy a tasting bottle and your fee is refunded.)\nFeatured Wines:\n- Jeff Runquist "R" Zinfandel 2023 - $26.99 - Blackberry\, black raspberry\, briary fruit and toasted oak with a generous\, smooth finish.\n- Jeff Runquist "R" Petite Sirah 2024 - $30.99 - Blackberry\, plum\, cassis\, cocoa and baking spice with rounded tannins and a full body.\n- Jeff Runquist "R" Barbera 2024 - $26.99 - Red cherry\, raspberry\, blueberry and spice with bright acidity and a lively finish.\n- Jeff Runquist "R" Cabernet Franc 2024 - $28.99 - Black cherry\, raspberry\, violet and subtle pepper with a smooth\, savory finish.\nCome explore Jeff Runquist Wines and find your favorite bottle. Buy a tasting bottle and your fee is refunded.
LOCATION:85 Foothill Rd Ste 1 Reno\, NV 89511
SUMMARY:Jeff Runquist Tasting
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR